function receiveJSON(){
    var files = []
 
    fetch('http://localhost:3001/receiveJSON')
    .then(res =>res.json())
    .then(data => files.push(data))
    var a = []
    a.push(files[0])
    console.log(files[0][0])
    return files
    
}

export default receiveJSON;
